                    <span>I have enough programming books that if weighed would weigh as much as a car.<P>I love this book.<P>The best part is that I can read it and follow the examples without having to sit at my computer.<P>The key word in the title is beginning. I have found it to be a great foundation book on its subject matter.<P>The authors should get an atta boy for this one.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Great for Beginers... Good reference</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
